 This is at the GM's discretion.
 In extraordinary circumstances, he may allow none, or multiples per PC,
 or perhaps only for some PCs.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Some skills grant additional powers at certain levels.
 Others simply increase.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Normally these skill bumps cannot be 
