\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A common type of ceremony designed to assure eternal favor for the dead.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
Sermon
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As most priests function as a deity's spokesperson, priests are usually
 expected to keep the faithful in line.
