\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Connections: Underworld, City of X
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

several towns adjacent to Y
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is much more believable.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The player is free to characterize this in any manner he feels would add
 flavor and color.
 A good example of this would be the London homeless network that Sherlock
 Holmes uses for information gathering.
\end_layout

