 in some action.
 Compensation is usually offered, either implicitly or explicitly, but generally
 not required, as the closeness of this relationship is such that the acquaintan
ce may also ask such a favor of the PC.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Order - An order is demanding something of someone, without specific recompense
 offered.
